Package lib.homies.framework.spigot.utils

Class SpigotItemBuilder

java.lang.Object
lib.homies.framework.spigot.utils.SpigotItemBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
ItemBuilder
public class SpigotItemBuilder extends Object implements ItemBuilder
Spigot-specific implementation of the ItemBuilder interface. This class uses Bukkit's ItemStack and ItemMeta to construct items with various properties, adhering to the platform-agnostic API.
